data.description: This bi-level home in town offers 5 spacious bedrooms or opportunity to have a private separate living quarters or the potential for two rentals.  The main home has  4 bedrooms with 2  baths, an updated Kitchen, featuring all new Stainless appliances, countertops, backsplash and Luxury Vinyl floors. There is a dining area which could also be used as an office and a bright open living room with a charming fireplace.  The main level has refinished hardwood floors. The step down level has a second oversized family room, with an addition which offers a separate private entrance, the 5th bedroom suite which includes another 1.5 baths and the potential to make a kitchenette. In this space, the refrigerator is already in place.  There is a laundry room which could be shared plus a walk-in closet.  The basement provides lots of space for additional storage plus a 2nd laundry hook-up.  There is a spacious back yard, a covered porch with a patio,  2 sheds and the yard is fully fenced.  There is so much potential and space.  A Brand New roof is being installed. This home is located minutes from I81, the restaurants, shopping and hospital.  Plus, War Memorial Park which is across the street features an outdoor pool facility, picnic pavilions, tennis courts, miniature golf and multiple playgrounds.  Call today for an appointment!
